title: How to open replay file
body:
Hi guys:

just find out new open beta have a official  feature to replay the game I just played, with record  function, saved video will under Highlight folder with _*.webm_ extension can be open  with firefox.

The replay file extension  is  _*.rofl_  (YES, is ROFL~~~ Replay Of Lol) under Replays folder.
Now I can't really find any program to open this _ROFL_  file.

Some one or Riot can provide a player to play it?

TY
